Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:29.01,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(494,510)}Tradução para português\N{\fs40}RAFAEL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:40.72,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\pos(286,455)}Timing\N{\fs40}Galaxy 9000\N\N{\fs}Time-checking\N{\fs40}Sewil
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:44.16,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,0)\pos(762,278)}Quality-checking\N{\fs40}Sewil\NGalaxy 9000\NHalee
